{"tid":955012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"癡漢國中生?趁電車抖動　跟女高中生親密接觸","createTime":"2018-12-25T05:35:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T06:05:06.000Z","uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"86ccb6a46a45219c364b94f2e21dc1963f6da6d5","tid":955012,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:35:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181224/1489071\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181224%2F1489071&d=alT2BSZizqkq1jNfek8Te%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=3ee839db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181224%2F1489071&h=3825fa27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181224/1489071</a><br />\n<br />\n日本一名國中男生，用不小心將書本撒落一地、被電車震到站不穩的方法，去偷看、偷碰搭車的女高中生，結果全程都被同車廂的乘客拍下來了。<br />\n<br />\n日本網友「けーと」在《推特》分享影片指出，她搭電車的時候，看到一名男國中生，多次用打開書包，將書包內的課本等物品散落一地的手法，偷看站在前方的女高中生美腿，甚至還趁著電車震動的時候，假裝站不穩，整個身體往女高中生的身體靠過去，讓她表示「這傢伙太危險了」。<br />\n<br />\n網友看到後紛紛留言「不能怪他，這時是性慾最盛期」、「應該是想看內褲齁」、「擁有可媲美足球選手的演技」、「最後那個女高中生感覺挺可愛的」、「這是在大阪的阪急寶塚本線?」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pYKQczb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpYKQczb.jpg&h=049c7ae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網址內有影片<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條友d演技好迫真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6f9b325b5c9431f517912a7fba14b90c0c1a38","tid":955012,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:44:39.000Z","msg":"wow唔識串"},{"pid":"6a7ed865fe80a8d3c1cb0829b908ba25ff5c8e9e","tid":955012,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e95c241a66698a2092371